  "summary": {
    "as": "Introduced in House",
    "asOf": "2023-01-31",
    "date": "2023-05-28T22:14:41Z",
    "text": "This resolution calls for the Department of State to designate Nigeria as a country of particular concern for egregious violations of religious freedom. It also states that the President should appoint a Special Envoy for Nigeria and the Lake Chad Region with the rank of Ambassador to monitor and combat atrocities there."
